#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.mod.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.mod"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:1 of
msgid "Return element-wise remainder of division."
msgstr "返回逐元素的除法余数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:3 of
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Computes the remainder complementary to the `floor_divide` function.  It "
"is equivalent to the Python modulus operator``x1 % x2`` and has the same "
"sign as the divisor `x2`. The MATLAB function equivalent to "
"``np.remainder`` is ``mod``."
msgstr ""
"计算与 `floor_divide` 函数互补的余数。它等价于 Python 的取模运算符 ``x1 %"
" x2``，并且符号与除数 `x2` 相同。与 ``np.remainder`` 等价的 MATLAB 函数是"
" ``mod``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:10 of
msgid "This should not be confused with:"
msgstr "不要将其与以下内容混淆："

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:12 of
msgid ""
"Python 3.7's `math.remainder` and C's ``remainder``, which computes the "
"IEEE remainder, which are the complement to ``round(x1 / x2)``."
msgstr ""
"Python 3.7 的 `math.remainder` 和 C 的 ``remainder``，它们计算的是 IEEE "
"余数，是 ``round(x1 / x2)`` 的互补运算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:15 of
msgid ""
"The MATLAB ``rem`` function and or the C ``%`` operator which is the "
"complement to ``int(x1 / x2)``."
msgstr ""
"MATLAB 的 ``rem`` 函数或 C 的 ``%`` 运算符，它们是 ``int(x1 / x2)`` 的"
"互补运算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:18 of
msgid "Dividend array."
msgstr "被除数数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:20 of
msgid "Divisor array."
msgstr "除数数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:22 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供了该参数，则其形状必须可以广播到输入形状。"
"如果未提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的 tensor。元组（只能作为关键字"
"参数）的长度必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:27 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:32 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- The element-wise remainder of the quotient ``floor_divide(x1, "
"x2)``. Returns a scalar if both  `x1` and `x2` are scalars."
msgstr ""
"**y** -- 逐元素的商 ``floor_divide(x1, x2)`` 的余数。如果 `x1` 和 `x2` 都"
"是标量，则返回一个标量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:38 of
msgid ":py:obj:`floor_divide`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:39 of
msgid "Equivalent of Python ``//`` operator."
msgstr "等价于 Python 的 ``//`` 运算符。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:41 of
msgid ":py:obj:`divmod`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:42 of
msgid "Simultaneous floor division and remainder."
msgstr "同时进行向下取整除法和求余。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:44 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fmod`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:45 of
msgid "Equivalent of the MATLAB ``rem`` function."
msgstr "等价于 MATLAB 的 ``rem`` 函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:47 of
msgid ":py:obj:`divide`, :py:obj:`floor`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:50 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.mod.mod:51 of
msgid "Returns 0 when `x2` is 0 and both `x1` and `x2` are (tensors of) integers."
msgstr "当 `x2` 为 0 且 `x1` 和 `x2` 都是（tensor 的）整数时，返回 0。"

